Hi, and welcome to the world of Kita,

Basically, there isnt much you should know.
Experience with gentoo linux and portage would be very useful.

Requirements:
  Ruby 1.9.1+
  Rake

To install, please run:

  rake kitaman:install['prefix']

For any questions please email Kirill R (you should know how)

All the best

Kirill R
